#13. Program to find the Simple Interest and the total amount when the Principal, Rate of Interest 
#and Time are entered by the user.

p=eval(input("enter principal amount: "))
r=eval(input("enter rate of interest per month: "))
t=eval(input("enter time in month: "))

SI=(p*r*t)/100
T=p + SI

print(f''' simple interest is {SI}
       and total amount is {T}''')
       
